This paper is about improving user experience in similarity search, which is a common problem in information retrieval (IR) and database (DB) systems. Therefore, cs.IR and cs.DB are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes algorithms that involve machine learning techniques, such as clustering and optimization, which are relevant to sub-categories cs.CL, cs.AI, and cs.LG.
